description:
&lt;p&gt;The opportunity has arisen for a full-time Domestic Supervisor to join our Domestic Services Team. The post-holder will be able to gain experience of working in a rewarding department as part of Harrogate Integrated Facilities who offer services directly to Harrogate NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The main duties and responsibilities of the post holder will be to provide leadership and administrative support to domestic service department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will include managing the day to day running of the department and being a first line contact dealing with any queries or concerns that are reported to the office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Examples of other duties for this role will include management and allocation of staff, monitoring cleaning standards, 1-2-1 meetings with staff and the recruitment, training and induction of new team members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel this role would be suitable for yourself, please take a further look at the attached job description or if you have any further queries please contact Adrian Kopycinski on 01423 555340 or via email at Adrian.kopycinski@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;** Previous applicants that have applied for this role in the last 3 months need not apply **&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAdrian KopycinskiJob titleActing Hotel &amp; Site Services ManagerEmail addressAdrian.kopycinski@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
